{"tid":1700734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連日事件證明全民開cam 係非常重要","createTime":"2019-11-08T16:03:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T07:56:25.000Z","uid":65045,"like":60,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"533f1ee33bf57ed8b4822687fdb632b213b74d35","tid":1700734,"uid":65045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T16:03:44.000Z","msg":"1. 屋企有機會俾狗搔擾嘅，set 一個cctv對住門口<br />\n<br />\n2. 所有車主無論泊邊，set 24小時前後cam<br />\n<br />\n3. 出街發夢嘅帶go pro <br />\n<br />\n4. 和理同街坊就算路過，相機都要隨時ready. 有狗喺視線範圍要開定cam, 唔好等有動作先影<br />\n<br />\n5. 喺屋企嘅手足見到樓下或附近有咩動靜即刻影低，啲狗以為暗角冇人見特別猖狂<br />\n<br />\n啲黑警冇人性，隨時隨地都可以冇任何預警下咬人，有事先問有冇人影到已經太遲，video 影多咗可以隨時delete, 但出事冇影到就冇得返轉頭，唔好依賴記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c213f999a7ca8ba01dc87fce9853cd4dbc70da9","tid":1700734,"uid":65045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T16:05:08.000Z","msg":"甴近平一隻"},{"pid":"094b000ec7bcbb4cf89c7c544e6ee7eb96c30880","tid":1700734,"uid":65045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T16:05:26.000Z","msg":"甴近平兩隻"},{"pid":"6871fd2036267de692c1ddca9e822c46bbb1afe8","tid":1700734,"uid":65045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T16:06:13.000Z","msg":"甴近平三隻"},{"pid":"9b412ce0e73b6e7a75cd4555f06991fc419181ab","tid":1700734,"uid":65045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T16:07:42.000Z","msg":"甴近平四隻"},{"pid":"144afd3fc99848c5a4b2135d2c9128f9813ec591","tid":1700734,"uid":20262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T16:07:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"281360989eeb44b04617ce123920d3d0ee3e1c79","tid":1700734,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T16:08:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a7ce437e776fd821fbf7d62185fdcb5e435def9","tid":1700734,"uid":115538,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T16:09:22.000Z","msg":"出街發夢帶go pro會唔會反而害到手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wond